  "description": "A breathtaking landscape featuring Yosemite Falls cascading down a towering granite cliff face. The falls appear as a shimmering white ribbon against the dark grey of the rock. Below, a lush green meadow stretches out, dotted with trees in full spring foliage. The trees vary in shades of vibrant green, creating depth. In the background, more forested mountains rise, partially obscured by soft, white clouds. The sky is a mix of blue and cloudy grey, providing a dramatic backdrop. The overall composition evokes a sense of grandeur and natural beauty.",
